# Implementation Plan: Issues Module

> Derived from: `docs/spec-issues-module.md`
> Status: Ready for implementation

---

## Overview

Build a configurable Issues module (problem log) across 17 tasks in 3 phases.
The feature adds `Issue` as a first-class domain entity alongside `Risk` and
`ChangeRequest`, with bidirectional links to both, a configurable category list
in Settings, a full register + detail + form UI, and no new permissions (reuses
`risks:*`).

**Total files touched:** 17 (9 modified, 3 new pages, 5 modified pages/components)
**Phases:** A = data layer (no UI), B = core pages, C = integration wiring

