## Architecture Decisions

| Decision | Choice | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| Status change mechanism | Plain `PATCH` with `{ status }` | No approval chain needed; avoids a separate transition endpoint |
| Permissions | Reuse `risks:read` / `risks:update` / `risks:archive` | Zero migration cost; all 6 existing roles work unchanged |
| Cost field | Simple `estimatedCost: number` | No calendar profile needed; keeps the form lean |
| Issue reference prefix | `I###` | Follows `R###` / `C###` convention; unambiguous in linked-ref lists |
| Bidirectional sync | `syncIssueLinks()` in mock; server-enforced in HTTP | Mirrors existing `syncRiskLinks()` exactly |
| Issue categories | `AppConfig.issueCategories` configurable in Settings | Same pattern as `riskStatuses`, `changeCategories` |
| New page location | `src/pages/issues/` | Follows `src/pages/risks/` and `src/pages/changes/` layout |

