- [ ] `updateIssue` with `{ linkedRiskRefs: ["R001"] }` causes R001 to gain `"I001"` in `linkedIssueRefs`
- [ ] Removing a risk link on update removes the back-ref from that risk
- [ ] `archiveIssue` sets `archived: true`; issue disappears from `list()` filtered views
- [ ] `restoreIssue` sets `archived: false`
- [ ] Simulated 350ms latency matches other services

**Verification:**
- [ ] `npm run typecheck` — 0 errors
- [ ] `npm run build` — clean

**Dependencies:** Task 3 (interface), Task 4 (seed data)

