- [ ] `/issues/new` → `AddIssue`, guarded by `risks:update`
- [ ] `/issues/:ref` → `IssueDetail`, guarded by `risks:read`
- [ ] `/issues/:ref/edit` → `EditIssue`, guarded by `risks:update`
- [ ] Route `/issues/new` is not mistaken for a ref (order correct)
- [ ] Catch-all `*` route still redirects to `/dashboard`
- [ ] `Suspense` `<PageSkeleton />` fallback wraps all four routes (already handled by existing `<Suspense>` wrapper)

