## Risks and Mitigations

| Risk | Impact | Probability | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|---|
| `linkedIssueRefs` cascades to many files | High | High | Resolve all TS errors in Task 1 before moving on; do not skip the typecheck gate |
| `sanitizeConfig` misses the new field | High | Medium | Test by loading the app with a stale localStorage config (clear `issueCategories` from the stored JSON manually in DevTools) |
| `syncIssueLinks` diff logic incorrect | Medium | Medium | In Task 5, explicitly test: create with link, update to remove link, verify back-ref is removed |
| Route order: `/issues/new` treated as ref | Medium | Low | Register `/issues/new` before `/issues/:ref` in `App.tsx`; verified by navigating to "Raise Issue" |
| Portfolio stats line wraps on narrow sidebar | Low | Low | Test sidebar at default 230 px width; truncate with ellipsis if needed |
| `AppData` memoised value grows stale | Low | Low | Follow `useCallback` + `upsertIssue` pattern exactly; do not inline closures in the memoised value |

